{"title":"花街行（两首）","authors":["晓雪"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":7,"day":23}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"花街行（两首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晓雪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花街"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千家万户的爱好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四乡八寨的珍藏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖祖辈辈的传统，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫山遍野的春光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汇成这人间的奇景："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花街花城花的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奇花异卉数不清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩云紫雾如梦幻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比端午艳阳更热烈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比晴天朝霞更灿烂；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我感到春光浓于酒啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷醉在保山的花街上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百样花枝吸引我的目光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千般香味扑进我的鼻腔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万分激动的心却在思考："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国边疆的好山好水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辛勤园丁的匠心独运，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天才花工的奇思妙想……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比美"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"栀子花淡雅朴素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玫瑰花鲜红富丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"素馨兰风姿独具，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄缅桂芳香四溢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这边的花店缤纷多彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边的花展更加诱人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彝、白、傣、藏、回，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"傈僳、景颇、独龙、纳西……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各族少女都穿节日盛装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各地名花都来斗艳争奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与人比，花与花比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人与花比，花与人比；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比自然的美，比生活的美，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比美的创造，比美的风韵……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}